    • splitRawDataToMetadataAndPassageString

      private String[] splitRawDataToMetadataAndPassageString​(String rawData)
      Splits the full hecc code into a string with the metadata and a string with everything afterwards
      Parameters:
      rawData - the raw hecc data
      Returns:
      an array with 2 indexes. index 0 holds the metadata string (everything before 1st passage declaration). index 1 holds everything from the 1st passage declaration onwards.
